data.name: GetQueryDataGrid
data.value: SELECT [l].[idtipoLista],[w].[WarrantyGarId] AS [warrantyId], [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] AS [warrantyDetailId], [w].[WarrantyCode], [w].[WarrantyNumber], [w].[WarrantyType], [w].[Currency], [w].[Amount], [w].[Balance], [w].[Applied], [b].[bancoID] AS [financialEntityId], [b].[codigoBanco] AS [financialEntityCode], [b].[nombreBanco] AS [financialEntityName], [c].[empresaID] AS [companyId], [c].[codigo] AS [companyCode], [c].[nombre] AS [companyName], [c].[nombreCorto] AS [companyShortName], COALESCE(([c].[nombreCorto] + ' - ') + [a].[Agent], N'') AS [companyAgent], COALESCE(([c].[codigo] + ' - ') + [a].[Agent], N'') AS [companyAgentId], [w].[InitialWarrantyDate], [w].[FinalWarrantyDate], [dw].[AdmissionDate], [vbw].[FinalDate] AS [validFinalDate], [l].[codigo] AS [status],[a].[Agent],[l].[nombre] as statusname FROM [Warranty].[WarrantiesGar] AS [w] inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyDetailGar] AS [dw] ON [w].[WarrantyGarId] = [dw].[WarrantyGarId] inner JOIN [Warranty].[BankWarrantyGar] AS [bw] ON [w].[WarrantyGarId] = [bw].[WarrantyGarId] inner JOIN [banco].[Banco] AS [b] ON [bw].[FinancialEntity] = [b].[codigoBanco] inner JOIN [agente].[Empresa] AS [c] ON [bw].[Company] = [c].[codigo] inner JOIN [Warranty].[ValidBankWarrantyGar] AS [vbw] ON [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] = [vbw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyAgentGar] AS [a] ON [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] = [a].[WarrantyDetailGarId] inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyTrackingGar] AS [t] ON [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] = [t].[WarrantyDetailGarId] inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyDetailApplicationGar] AS [dap] ON [dw].[WarrantyGarId] = [dap].[WarrantyGarId] inner JOIN [transversal].[Lista] AS [l] ON [dap].[StatusCode] = [l].[codigo] {0} AND [l].[idtipolista] = 97 group by [l].[idtipolista],[w].[WarrantyGarId], [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId], [w].[WarrantyCode], [w].[WarrantyNumber], [w].[WarrantyType], [w].[Currency], [w].[Amount], [w].[Balance], [w].[Applied], [b].[bancoID] , [b].[codigoBanco] , [b].[nombreBanco] , [c].[empresaID] , [c].[codigo] , [c].[nombre] , [c].[nombreCorto] , COALESCE(([c].[nombreCorto] + ' - ') + [a].[Agent], N'') , COALESCE(([c].[codigo] + ' - ') + [a].[Agent], N'') , [w].[InitialWarrantyDate], [w].[FinalWarrantyDate], [dw].[AdmissionDate], [vbw].[FinalDate], [l].[codigo],[a].[Agent] ,[l].[nombre] ORDER BY [w].[WarrantyNumber] DESC

data.name: ImportsExportsExpirationTransfer
data.value: select Business, TypeData, DateExpiration, CompanyId from load.ImportsExportsExpirationTransfer IEET where IEET.Business = '{0}' and IEET.TypeData = {1} and IEET.DateExpiration = '{2}' and IEET.CompanyId = {3}

data.name: InvoiceDebtorsInformation
data.value: SELECT [w].[WarrantyNumber], [c].[nombreCorto] AS [companyShortName], sp.ExpirationDate, b.nombreBanco as BankName, sp.TotalDebt as ValueDebt, CAST(CAST(w.Amount AS NUMERIC) AS FLOAT) as Amount, FORMAT(w.FinalWarrantyDate, 'yyyy-MM-yy') as Validity FROM [Warranty].[WarrantiesGar] AS [w] inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyDetailGar] AS [dw] ON [w].[WarrantyGarId] = [dw].[WarrantyGarId] inner JOIN [Warranty].[BankWarrantyGar] AS [bw] ON [w].[WarrantyGarId] = [bw].[WarrantyGarId] inner JOIN [banco].[Banco] AS [b] ON [bw].[FinancialEntity] = [b].[codigoBanco] inner JOIN [agente].[Empresa] AS [c] ON [bw].[Company] = [c].[codigo] inner JOIN [Warranty].[ValidBankWarrantyGar] AS [vbw] ON [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] = [vbw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyAgentGar] AS [a] ON [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] = [a].[WarrantyDetailGarId] inner join [Payment].[SupplyLimitation] sp on a.Agent= sp.AgentCode inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyTrackingGar] AS [t] ON [dw].[WarrantyDetailGarId] = [t].[WarrantyDetailGarId] inner JOIN [Warranty].[WarrantyDetailApplicationGar] AS [dap] ON [dw].[WarrantyGarId] = [dap].[WarrantyGarId] inner JOIN [transversal].[Lista] AS [l] ON [dap].[StatusCode] = [l].[codigo] where l.idTipoLista = 97 and StatusCode = 1 and sp.ExpirationDate = '{0}' group by [w].[WarrantyNumber], [c].[nombreCorto], sp.ExpirationDate, b.nombreBanco, sp.TotalDebt, w.Amount, w.FinalWarrantyDate ORDER BY [w].[WarrantyNumber] DESC

data.name: QueryBank
data.value: select b.[bancoID] FROM [banco].[CuentaBancaria] ba inner join [banco].[Banco] b on ba.[entidadBancariaId] = b.[bancoID] where ba.[cuentaBancariaID] = {0}

data.name: QueryCompany
data.value: SELECT [E].[empresaID] AS [CompanyId], [E].[nit] AS [Nit], [E].[nombre] AS [CompanyName], [E].[fechaCreacion] AS [CreationDate], [E].[fechaModificacion] AS [ModificationDate], [E].[idUsuarioCrea] AS [CreationUser], [E].[idUsuarioActualiza] AS [ModificationUser], [E].[codigo] AS [CompanyCode], [E].[nombreCorto] AS [ShortName] FROM [agente].[Empresa] E WHERE [E].[codigo] = {0}

data.name: SqlCloseNationalGridOne
data.value: select tot.AgentCode,tot.companyShortname,tot.period,sum(tot.BankingCOP) as BankingCOP,sum(tot.Expiration) as Expiration, sum(tot.PrepaidValue) as PrepaidValue, sum(0) as Balance from ( select ed.AgentCode, c.nombreCorto as companyShortName,ed.expirationDetailGarId, (select sum(wp.ValueFrozenApplied - wp.ValueReturnsApplied) from warranty.WarrantyPaymentAppliedGar as wp inner join load.LoadExpirationDetailgar led on wp.ExpirationDetailGarId = led.ExpirationDetailGarId where wp.expirationdetailGarid = ed.ExpirationDetailGarId and led.InvoiceExpirationDate = @expirationDate) as BankingCOP,sum(ed.ValueRequested) as Expiration , Sum(ed.FrozenValue) as PrepaidValue,@period as period from load.LoadExpirationDetailgar ed inner join load.loadexpirationgar e on ed.expirationGarId = e.expirationGarId inner join agente.agente a on ed.AgentCode =a.codigoAgente join agente.empresa c on a.empresaid = c.empresaID where ed.InvoiceExpirationDate = @expirationDate ANd e.Scheme NOT IN('TIES','TIESEXTRA') and dbo.FnValidateSchemaAgent(e.Scheme,a.agenteID,e.ExpirationDate)='S' and MONTH(ed.DateStart) =@Month and YEAR(ed.DateStart) =@Year AND ed.ValueRequested <> 0 group by ed.AgentCode, c.nombreCorto,ed.expirationDetailGarId) as tot group by tot.AgentCode,tot.companyShortName,tot.period

data.name: SqlCloseNationalGridTwo
data.value: select tot.AgentCode,tot.companyShortname,tot.expirationdate,sum(tot.OutStandingBalance) as OutStandingBalance from ( select ed.AgentCode, c.nombreCorto as companyShortName,ed.InvoiceExpirationDate as expirationdate, sum(ed.ValuePending) as OutStandingBalance , Sum(ed.FrozenValue) as PrepaidValue,@Period as period from load.LoadExpirationDetailgar ed inner join load.loadexpirationgar e on ed.expirationGarId = e.expirationGarId inner join agente.agente a on ed.AgentCode =a.codigoAgente join agente.empresa c on a.empresaid = c.empresaID where ed.InvoiceExpirationDate =@ExpirationDate ANd e.Scheme NOT IN('TIES','TIESEXTRA') and dbo.FnValidateSchemaAgent(e.Scheme,a.agenteID,e.ExpirationDate)='S' and MONTH(ed.DateStart) =@Month and YEAR(ed.DateStart) =@Year AND ed.ValueRequested <> 0 and ed.ValuePending <> 0 group by ed.AgentCode, c.nombreCorto,ed.InvoiceExpirationDate) as tot group by tot.AgentCode,tot.companyShortname,tot.expirationdate
